data.name: Asian Sesame Salad
data.quickTastyDescription: A fresh and crunchy salad with a delightful sesame dressing, perfect for a light meal or side.
detailedCookingInstructions: In a large bowl, combine the mixed salad greens, shredded carrots, cucumber, red bell pepper, and edamame.
In a separate bowl, whisk together soy sauce, rice vinegar, honey, sesame oil, and minced ginger to create the dressing.
Pour the dressing over the salad and toss gently to combine.
Sprinkle sesame seeds on top, add salt and pepper to taste, and serve immediately.
data.detailedName: Asian Sesame Salad with Crunchy Vegetables
